{
  "stem": "512.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never went for checkups or anything to any German doctor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just when I was giving birth, I went to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And David was born.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was still very, very-- still wasn't-- not in good shape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't nurse him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was no refrigeration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was no food for him so he became very sick.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he was two weeks old, and he had to put him back in the hospital because he was vomiting and diarrhea he had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the German doctors, they couldn't care less.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And you didn't have confidence in them in the first place because you feared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they didn't kill you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They might kill you now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had a very, very rough time with David-- very rough time in one room without refrigeration in the summer.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was so very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody-- there was a lady that gave birth, and she was able to nurse her child, so she felt sorry for me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she took David, and she was nursing David.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that saved his life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then the camp was liberated, I think, in 1948 or 49'.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went to another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, the same thing-- little room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from there we went to the Bergen-Belsen, because we couldn't immigrate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The quota was so big-- first we couldn't-- we had relatives, but the quota was very big.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to wait a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So but then we came through the Jewish-- the Joint.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We came-- they sponsored us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in 1950, we came to this country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they sent us-- the joint sent us to Bangor, Maine.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
